    <item>
      <title>亚洲美元债券销售创 2016 年以来最差开局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/dollar-bond-sales-in-asia-see-worst-start-to-year-since-2016</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着地区借款人在国内筹集更便宜的资金并等待美联储降息，亚洲的美元债券销售迎来了八年来最疲软的开局，与强劲的全球趋势相反。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/dollar-bond-sales-in-asia-see-worst-start-to-year-since-2016</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国证券交易委员会推迟对对冲基金交易商注册规则的投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/sec-postpones-vote-on-dealer-registration-rule-for-hedge-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会推迟了对最终规则的投票，该规则要求许多对冲基金和自营交易公司注册为交易商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/sec-postpones-vote-on-dealer-registration-rule-for-hedge-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 22:48:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国科技巨头股价下跌；亚洲股市低开：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[微软公司和Alphabet公司在公布财报后尾盘下跌，导致纳斯达克100指数期货暴跌。亚洲股市基准将小幅下跌。]]></description>
