    <item>
      <title>沃尔玛将股票分割为 1 股 3 股；股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/walmart-wmt-sets-3-for-1-stock-split-citing-employees-shares-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沃尔玛公司宣布进行一拆三的股票分割，称较低的价格将有助于更多员工购买股票。]]></description>
